# 🎨 **DRAWMASTER - MULTIPLAYER DRAWING GUESS GAME COMPLETED!**

## 🎯 **OVERVIEW**

Successfully transformed DrawMaster into a **complete multiplayer drawing guess game** based on the provided Gartic.io-style interface. The game now features professional drawing tools, real-time chat system, multiplayer player management, and engaging gameplay mechanics.

## ✅ **MAJOR FEATURES IMPLEMENTED**

### **🎮 Complete Game Flow**
```
Login → Initial Screen (History + Rules) → Waiting Room → Multiplayer Game → Results → Loop
```

### **👥 Multiplayer Interface (Image-Based Design)**
- ✅ **Left Panel**: Player list with avatars, scores, and drawing indicators
- ✅ **Right Panel**: Canvas, tools, progress bars, and dual chat system
- ✅ **Header**: Game title, timer, and progress tracking
- ✅ **Professional Layout**: Matches the provided reference image

### **🎨 Advanced Drawing System**
- ✅ **Drawing Canvas**: 780x320px professional drawing area
- ✅ **Drawing Tools**: Pencil, Eraser, Fill bucket with visual feedback
- ✅ **Color Palette**: 12 colors with selection highlighting
- ✅ **Brush Size**: Adjustable 1-15px with real-time preview
- ✅ **Clear Function**: Confirmation dialog for safety
- ✅ **Smooth Drawing**: Anti-aliased lines with round caps

### **💬 Dual Chat System**
- ✅ **Answer Tab**: Dedicated guess input and history
- ✅ **Chat Tab**: General communication area
- ✅ **Real-time Messages**: Instant message display
- ✅ **System Messages**: Game events and notifications
- ✅ **Auto-scroll**: Always shows latest messages

### **⚡ Game Mechanics**
- ✅ **Timer System**: 60-second countdown with visual progress
- ✅ **Progress Bars**: Header and canvas progress indicators
- ✅ **Word Bank**: Vietnamese word collection
- ✅ **Scoring System**: Time-based scoring (timeLeft × 2)
- ✅ **Round Management**: Multi-round gameplay
- ✅ **Guess Detection**: Automatic correct answer recognition

