## 🛠️ **TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION**

### **🎨 Drawing Engine**
```csharp
✅ Bitmap Canvas: 780x320px with white background
✅ Graphics Object: GDI+ with anti-aliasing
✅ Pen Customization: Color, size, line caps
✅ Mouse Events: Down, Move, Up with smooth tracking
✅ Real-time Rendering: Immediate visual feedback
✅ Memory Management: Proper bitmap disposal
```

### **👥 Multiplayer System**
```csharp
✅ Player Management: Dynamic player list with avatars
✅ Role Indicators: Visual drawing state indicators
✅ Score Tracking: Individual player scores
✅ Avatar Colors: Unique color assignments
✅ Trophy System: Visual rewards for top players
```

### **💬 Chat Architecture**
```csharp
✅ Dual Panel System: Answer + Chat separation
✅ Message History: Scrollable text areas
✅ Input Handling: Enter key submission
✅ Placeholder Text: Professional input fields
✅ System Messages: Game event notifications
```

### **⏰ Timer & Progress**
```csharp
✅ Timer Object: 1-second interval updates
✅ Progress Bars: Header + canvas synchronized
✅ Color Coding: Green → Orange → Red progression
✅ Visual Feedback: Time-based UI changes
✅ Automatic Progression: Round advancement
```

## 🎯 **GAME FEATURES BREAKDOWN**

### **🎨 Drawing Tools Features**
| Tool | Function | Visual Feedback | Shortcuts |
|------|----------|----------------|-----------|
| ✏️ Pencil | Primary drawing | Blue highlight when active | Default tool |
| 🧽 Eraser | Remove content | Red highlight, larger size | 2x brush size |
| 🪣 Fill | Flood fill | Green highlight | Future feature |
| 🎨 Colors | 12-color palette | Golden border selection | Visual preview |
| 📏 Size | 1-15px brush | Real-time size display | Trackbar control |
| 🗑️ Clear | Canvas reset | Confirmation dialog | Safety feature |

### **💬 Chat System Features**
| Feature | Answer Tab | Chat Tab | Functionality |
|---------|------------|----------|---------------|
| 📝 Input | Guess submission | General chat | Enter key support |
| 📜 History | Guess attempts | System messages | Auto-scroll |
| 🎯 Detection | Word matching | N/A | Automatic scoring |
| 🔔 Notifications | Success alerts | Join/leave events | Real-time updates |

### **👥 Player Management**
| Element | Visual | Information | Status |
|---------|--------|-------------|--------|
| 🎨 Avatar | Colored circles | Unique per player | Drawing indicator |
| 📛 Name | Bold text | Player identity | Truncated if long |
| 🏆 Score | Blue text | Current points | Trophy for top players |
| ✏️ Drawing | Golden border | Active drawer | Pencil icon overlay |

