## 🔧 **TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS**

### **🏗️ Architecture**
```
Form1 (Main Container)
├── Header Panel (Title + Timer)
├── Content Panel
│   ├── Players Panel (Left)
│   │   ├── Player List
│   │   └── Avatars + Scores
│   └── Game Area Panel (Right)
│       ├── Warning Panel
│       ├── Drawing Canvas
│       ├── Drawing Tools
│       ├── Progress Bar
│       └── Chat Area
│           ├── Answer Tab
│           └── Chat Tab
```

### **🎮 Game State Management**
```csharp
✅ Login State: User authentication
✅ Initial State: History and rules display
✅ Waiting State: Player preparation
✅ Playing State: Active game session
✅ Results State: Score display and reset
```

### **💾 Data Management**
```csharp
✅ Player Data: Names, scores, drawing status
✅ Game Data: Timer, rounds, current word
✅ Chat Data: Message history and types
✅ Drawing Data: Canvas bitmap and pen settings
✅ Settings Data: Persistent user preferences
```

